vior text does not require external network/subprocess/OS primitives beyond local persistence supported at Integration level. No AI/ML dependence.","test_description":"Instantiate the real persistent queue backend with a small configured capacity, enqueue up to limit, then attempt one additional enqueue and assert deterministic rejection plus unchanged persisted depth.","plan_consistent":true,"plan_consistent_note":null,"level_probabilities":{"Unit":0.06,"Integration":0.69,"System":0.24,"Agentic":0.01,"Workflow":0.0}}]}
